{"data":[{"date":"07:42 16/07","title":"Gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Varane s\u00e1nh ngang Beckenbauer v\u00e0 Carlos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Raphael Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVarane \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-2 d\u00e0nh cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u00f2n 20 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ndash; m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Raphael Varane, danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (Champions League/ Europa League) l\u1eabn World Cup trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 9 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/gianh-chuc-vo-dich-varane-di-vao-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Varane l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Varane \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1 l\u00e0 Luka Modric. Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Varane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic, b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sami Khedira, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 World Cup 2014 &ndash; nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br>\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;&#10; mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;background:#FFFFCC;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\"><br>\r\n            D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh   s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap <strong>c\u00fap</strong>&nbsp;<strong>ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 World Cup</strong> trong 1 n\u0103m (\u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3   2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng):<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">1974: Sepp Maier,   Paul Breitner, Hans-Georg Schwarzenbeck, Franz Beckenbauer, Gerd Muller, Uli   Hoeness (Bayern &amp; T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">1998: Christian   Karembeu (Real Madrid &amp; Ph\u00e1p)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2002: Roberto   Carlos (Real Madrid &amp; Brazil)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2018: Raphael   Varane (Real Madrid &amp; Ph\u00e1p)<br>\r\n            &nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;&#10; mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"100%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:100.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;background:#FFFFCC;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0   danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap <strong>c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</strong><strong>&nbsp;v\u00e0 EURO</strong> trong 1 n\u0103m (\u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0   tr\u00ean):<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">1964: Luis Suarez   (Inter &amp; T\u00e2y Ban Nha)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">1988: Hans van   Breukelen, Ronald Koeman, Berry van Aerle, Gerald Vanenburg (PSV Eindhoven   &amp; H\u00e0 Lan)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2012: Fernando   Torres, Juan Mata (Chelsea &amp; T\u00e2y Ban Nha)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:&#10;  justify;line-height:normal\">2016: Cristiano   Ronaldo, Pepe (Real Madrid &amp; B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha)<br>\r\n            &nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-cdv-chay-vao-san-trong-tran-chung-ket-phap-vs-croatia-la-ai-421-191307.html\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n \u00edt ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup-421-191304.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup-421-191304.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mbappe, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &ldquo;si\u00eau xe&rdquo; v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, nh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1302","checkdouble":"191308"},{"date":"07:47 16/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (16/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1672018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;