t-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHazard &ldquo;c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u&rdquo; \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3, kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Meunier v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \u1edf Qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng anh h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c, sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ sau khi x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ sau khi x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Thibaut Courtois, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</span>, khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem clip Hazard tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i DJ ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/16/in3y8.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191268.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;v\u00f2i v\u0129nh&rdquo; Chelsea</span><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-bi-gianh-hang-ba-world-cup-cho-nhe-euro-2020-421-191212.html\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup: Ch\u1edd nh\u00e9 EURO 2020!</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba World Cup n\u0103m nay, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1300","checkdouble":"191314"},{"date":"08:49 16/07","title":"Griezmann ngh\u0129 sao khi \"Ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</span>, Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n anti-fan \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, m\u1ec9a mai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 Tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec Ch\u00e2u Phi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec Ch\u00e2u Phi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/griezmann-nghi-sao-khi-chau-phi-vo-dich-world-cup-khong-phai-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Ch\u00e2u Phi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ch\u00e2u Phi, v\u1edbi nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n do \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Les Bleus bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 da m\u00e0u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng Paul Pogba, Kylian Mbappe, Raphael Varane hay Samuel Umtiti\u2026<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea5y g\u00ec l\u00e0m vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u00f9i ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u0111i\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4n ngoan nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y ca ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid sau khi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi mi\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong s\u1ed1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi xa x\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi nhau, chia s\u1ebb chung suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018-421-191291.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-phap-dang-quang-world-cup-2018-421-191291.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1299","checkdouble":"191315"},{"date":"03:19 16/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Antoine Griezmann</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antoine Griezmann ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. S\u1ed1 7 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 52 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Binh-luan-Phap-vs-Croatia-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 2 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Griezmann ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018 (3 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, ch\u1ec9 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh cho Les Bleus l\u00e0 Michel Platini (14), Just Fontaine (13) v\u00e0 Thierry Henry (12).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Hugo Lloris</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t anh l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lloris co tinh huong xu ly loi\" title=\"Lloris c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd l\u1ed7i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/sai.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lloris m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng cho Mandzukic m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 69, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng th\u1eadt m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u00ean ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0th\u00ec l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mario Mandzukic, song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Mandzukic \u1eadp v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 nhanh khi\u1ebfn Lloris l\u00fang t\u00fang, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng bay th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Lloris l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 v\u00e0o tay Courtois c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9. R\u1ea5t may cho Lloris l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba dut diem cuc cang nang ty so len 3-1\" title=\"Pogba d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1eeb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 6 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Ph\u00e1p (55 l\u1ea7n), anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 35 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 86%. Pogba c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 2 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i nguy k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi, 3 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 cho Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic c\u1ee7a Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Pogba tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eeb Emmanuel Petit v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang Whoscored ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. Rio Ferdinand n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: N'Golo Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, N'Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ebb g\u1eaby nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Kante thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia vs Phap Modric va Kante\" title=\"Croatia vs Phap Modric va Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-Phap-4-2-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Ivan Rakitic v\u00e0 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Kante, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Kante \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh anh k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 Ivan Perisic trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-phap-42-croatia-421-191293.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</span> cho th\u1ea5y Kante c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n s\u1ed1 13 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 19 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 54%. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat anh ra ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Steven N'Zonzi, c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 sung s\u1ee9c h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kylian Mbappe</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y), anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 NHM ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe nhan giai thuong cau thu tre xuat sac nhat World Cup 2018\" title=\"Mbappe nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ki.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Mbappe khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ec7t nho\u00e0i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. Mbappe l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Pogba n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1 sau \u0111\u00f3 anh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 4-1.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y) l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, sau Pele cho Brazil n\u0103m 1958 (17 tu\u1ed5i 249 ng\u00e0y). C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mario Mandzukic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 109 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Mandzukic phan luoi nha\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Ivan-Rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 18, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Mandzukic trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. C\u00fa l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 17 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Subasic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Mandzukic gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ung dung tri\u1ec3n khai th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi d\u1eabn b\u00e0n. D\u00f9 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Hugo Lloris \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 2-4 th\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Mandzukic v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMario Mandzukic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sau Ernie Brandts c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan n\u0103m 1978. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Didier Deschamps</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, HLV Didier Deschamps ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps phat bieu ve tran Phap vs Croatia\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/des-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Deschamps g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 49 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn tung h\u1ebft b\u00e0i th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Deschamps c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 49 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n truy\u1ec1n cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDidier Deschamps tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV, sau Mario Zagallo c\u1ee7a Brazil v\u00e0 Franz Beckenbauer c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 20 n\u0103m Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 49 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1298","checkdouble":"191296"},{"date":"04:50 16/07","title":"QBV World Cup 2018: \"\u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qbv-world-cup-2018-dt-croatia-da-co-mot-giai-dau-dang-tu-hao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2>Croatia su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen t\u1eb7ng, khi anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec gi\u00e0nh QBV World Cup. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ecd, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. D\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/qbv-world-cup-2018-dt-croatia-da-co-mot-giai-dau-dang-tu-hao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 sau tr\u1eadn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Croatia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.&nbsp; Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Croatia&rdquo; &ndash; Modric chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Zlatko Dalic c\u0169ng h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi Modric \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup &ndash; nh\u01b0 Zidane, Maradona v\u00e0 Messi. \u0110T Croatia d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-didier-deschamps-noi-gi-khi-giup-phap-lan-thu-2-vo-dich-world-cup-421-191289.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-didier-deschamps-noi-gi-khi-giup-phap-lan-thu-2-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-didier-deschamps-noi-gi-khi-giup-phap-lan-thu-2-vo-dich-world-cup-421-191289.html\">HLV Didier Deschamps n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup?</span><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 49 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh Les Bleus x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-va-modric-duoc-vinh-danh-sau-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191288.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/mbappe-va-modric-duoc-vinh-danh-sau-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-va-modric-duoc-vinh-danh-sau-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191288.html\">Mbappe v\u00e0 Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nLuka Modric xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Kylian Mbappe nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1297","checkdouble":"191298"},{"date":"05:09 16/07","title":"Thua cay \u0111\u1eafng, sao Liverpool t\u1ed1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \"ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/thua-cay-dang-sao-liverpool-to-dt-phap-phan-bong-da.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng Kylian Mbapp \u2013 Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giroud ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Bay cao nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Bay cao nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Phap-vs-Croatia-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-Bay-cao-nho-cap-doi-vang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 546 ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. 80 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o, anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t ra kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Lovren v\u00e0 Vida b\u00ean ph\u00eda Croatia, anh c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh nh\u01b0 Mbappe hay Griezmann. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Giroud&nbsp;b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Nabil Fekir.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOlivier Giroud c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Nga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. Ng\u00f4i sao mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua 546 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps lu\u00f4n b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Giroud khi cho r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Giroud kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Giroud kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, song Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe va Griezmann toa sang giup Phap vo dich World Cup 2018\" title=\"Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng Kylian Mbapp &ndash; Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam. S\u1ed1 7 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 10 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, Antoine Griezmann ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 Mario Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m sau khi Ivan Perisic \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, ch\u1ec9 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh cho Les Bleus l\u00e0 Michel Platini (14), Just Fontaine (13) v\u00e0 Thierry Henry (12).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3, Mbappe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ivan Strinic b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, anh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf tinh t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Paul Pogba d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, Mbappe cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Lucas Hernandez, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 nh\u1ecbp ch\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c nhanh khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuc vo dich World Cup 2018 cua Phap co dong gop rat lon tu Mbappe va Griezmann\" title=\"Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/m10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a Mbappe (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, sau Pele cho Brazil n\u0103m 1958 (17 tu\u1ed5i 249 ng\u00e0y).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Griezmann, Mbappe d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 FIFA \u0111\u00e3 trao t\u1eb7ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2</span>, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK Euro 2016, Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann. Khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Les Bleus g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ph\u00e1p thua B\u0110N trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe va Griezmann la hien tai va tuong lai cua DT Phap\" title=\"Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/mba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf World Cup 2018, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Mbappe chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Griezmann c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mbappe, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00edch c\u1ef1c di chuy\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 7 tham gia r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Euro 2016, s\u1ed1 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (3 so v\u1edbi 4) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m (3.5 so v\u1edbi 5.6) c\u1ee7a Griezmann \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Griezmann ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i th\u1ea5p g\u1ea7n h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 Mbappe b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Griezmann chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 71.4% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGriezmann \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Mbappe \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 v\u0169 b\u00e3o \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Phap 4-2 Croatia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Thong-so-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1296","checkdouble":"191300"},{"date":"05:19 16/07","title":"Pogba: \u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup t\u1eeb th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft vang l\u00ean, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t cao. Les Bleus d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Croatia th\u00ec 6 l\u00e0 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 4 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p khi c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n song b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia \u0111\u1ea7y vui s\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia \u0111\u1ea7y vui s\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Phap-4-2-Croatia-day-vui-suong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau khi th\u1eafng Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, Paul Pogba c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1, b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. Anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Manchester United gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Pogba Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia \u0111\u1ea7y vui s\u01b0\u1edbng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNg\u00f4i sao th\u1ee9 2 (ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T Ph\u00e1p) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\u201d, Pogba n\u00f3i v\u1edbi k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh TF1. \u201cC\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t xinh \u0111\u1eb9p. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i! M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f3 90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 h\u00e3y l\u00e0m cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3! Hai \u0111\u1ed9i tranh t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-phap-42-croatia-421-191293.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-xuc-dong-sau-khi-cung-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-191292.html\">Griezmann x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-didier-deschamps-noi-gi-khi-giup-phap-lan-thu-2-vo-dich-world-cup-421-191289.html\">HLV Didier Deschamps n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191287.html\">Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1295","checkdouble":"191301"},{"date":"05:44 16/07","title":"Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i WC 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/mbappe-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Croatia \u1edf chung k\u1ebft cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 20 l\u1ea1i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMbappe t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay. \u1ede chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 Croatia, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c Cameroon \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y), ch\u1ec9 sau huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Pele (17 tu\u1ed5i 249 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/mbappe-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mbappe gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Anh g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 20 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ni\u1ec1m vui l\u1edbn, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau khi t\u1edbi World Cup l\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d, Mbappe n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe vo dich World Cup 2018\" title=\"Mbappe vo dich World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd qu\u00ean \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup khi ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i, Mbappe n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cL\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb sau Pele? Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn lao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i? Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi n\u00f3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bay cao v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191301.html\">Pogba: \u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191294.html\">HLV Croatia: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i hay ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thua Ph\u00e1p\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-phap-42-croatia-421-191293.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-xuc-dong-sau-khi-cung-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-191292.html\">Griezmann x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-rakitic-chi-ra-ly-do-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-191290.html\">Ivan Rakitic ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1294","checkdouble":"191302"},{"date":"05:37 16/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia: Les Bleus l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/du-am-phap-42-croatia-les-bleus-len-dinh-nho-cap-doi-hoan-hao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng Kylian Mbapp \u2013 Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giroud ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Bay cao nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Bay cao nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Phap-vs-Croatia-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-Bay-cao-nho-cap-doi-vang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 546 ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. 80 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o, anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t ra kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Lovren v\u00e0 Vida b\u00ean ph\u00eda Croatia, anh c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh nh\u01b0 Mbappe hay Griezmann. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Giroud&nbsp;b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Nabil Fekir.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOlivier Giroud c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Nga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. Ng\u00f4i sao mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua 546 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps lu\u00f4n b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Giroud khi cho r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Giroud kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Giroud kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, song Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe va Griezmann toa sang giup Phap vo dich World Cup 2018\" title=\"Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng Kylian Mbapp &ndash; Antoine Griezmann l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o Lam. S\u1ed1 7 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 10 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, Antoine Griezmann ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 Mario Mandzukic ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m sau khi Ivan Perisic \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, ch\u1ec9 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh cho Les Bleus l\u00e0 Michel Platini (14), Just Fontaine (13) v\u00e0 Thierry Henry (12).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3, Mbappe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ivan Strinic b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, anh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf tinh t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Paul Pogba d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, Mbappe cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Lucas Hernandez, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 nh\u1ecbp ch\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c nhanh khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuc vo dich World Cup 2018 cua Phap co dong gop rat lon tu Mbappe va Griezmann\" title=\"Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/m10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a Mbappe (19 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, sau Pele cho Brazil n\u0103m 1958 (17 tu\u1ed5i 249 ng\u00e0y).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Griezmann, Mbappe d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 FIFA \u0111\u00e3 trao t\u1eb7ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2</span>, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK Euro 2016, Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann. Khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Les Bleus g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ph\u00e1p thua B\u0110N trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe va Griezmann la hien tai va tuong lai cua DT Phap\" title=\"Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/mba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf World Cup 2018, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Mbappe chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Griezmann c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mbappe, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec t\u00edch c\u1ef1c di chuy\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 7 tham gia r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Euro 2016, s\u1ed1 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (3 so v\u1edbi 4) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m (3.5 so v\u1edbi 5.6) c\u1ee7a Griezmann \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Griezmann ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i th\u1ea5p g\u1ea7n h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 Mbappe b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Griezmann chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 71.4% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGriezmann \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 27 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Mbappe \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 v\u0169 b\u00e3o \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Phap 4-2 Croatia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Thong-so-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1293","checkdouble":"191303"},{"date":"05:42 16/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mbappe, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/khong-phai-mbappe-day-moi-la-cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201csi\u00eau xe\u201d v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, nh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAi l\u00e0 &ldquo;vua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9&rdquo;?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo. T\u00e2n binh 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, v\u1edbi 21,1 d\u1eb7m/gi\u1edd - kho\u1ea3ng 33,96 km/gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ebfp ngay sau CR7 \u1edf th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia. Anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t 33,77 km/gi\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh trong Top 10 vua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c \u0110T Anh &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 chung cu\u1ed9c. Trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m Marcus Rasford, Kyle Walker, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Cau-thu-chay-nhanh-nhat-World-Cup-2018-Khong-phai-Mbappe-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c kinh ho\u00e0ng &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 trong Top 10. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9&hellip; 37 trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 32,35 km/gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Mbappe b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, n\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi ph\u1ea3i theo k\u00e8m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn CR7, anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hattrick, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch Top 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 (th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb Daily Mail)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha): 33,96 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ante Rebic (Croatia): 33,77 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luis Advincula (Peru): 33,77 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford (Anh): 33,77 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Santiago Arias (Colombia): 33,64 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker (Anh): 33,47 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard (Anh): 33,47 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Meciej Rybus (Ba Lan): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marquinhos (Brazil): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling (Anh): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Laxalt (Uruguay): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aleksandr Golovin (Nga): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dani Carvajal (T\u00e2y Ban Nha): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano (Mexico): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hwang Hee Chan (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c): 33,31 km/gi\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&hellip;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe (Ph\u00e1p): 32,35 km/gi\u1edd</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-xuc-dong-sau-khi-cung-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-191292.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/griezmann-xuc-dong-sau-khi-cung-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-xuc-dong-sau-khi-cung-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-191292.html\">Griezmann x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191301.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191301.html\">Pogba: &ldquo;Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup t\u1eeb th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/croatia-nhung-nguoi-viet-nen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-croatia-461-191274.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia (Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup khi thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Les Bleus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1292","checkdouble":"191304"},{"date":"06:08 16/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p: \u201cC\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/lloris-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lloris m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn \u1edf chung k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Croatia \u0111\u1ea7y qu\u1eadt kh\u1edfi song \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann gi\u00fap Les Bleus d\u1eabn 2-1 sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n Croatia xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, h\u1ecd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Sau pha chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb v\u00e0 khi b\u1ecb \u00e1p s\u00e1t, anh chuy\u1ec1n th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Mario Mandzukic tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Hugo-Lloris-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Phap-4-2-Croatia-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lloris m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 20 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho sai l\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Hugo Lloris trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 hi\u1ebfm. \u1ede Tottenham hay Ph\u00e1p, anh \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Khi Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia, anh tin r\u1eb1ng sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chung c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vo dich World Cup 2018\" title=\"Phap vo dich World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/lloris-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m\u201d, Lloris n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i? \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 1-1 c\u01a1. Khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 4-1, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m \u0111i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho t\u00f4i.\u201d\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng ngay trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 2, tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng. Th\u1eadt vui khi th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi, b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-42-croatia-les-bleus-len-dinh-nho-cap-doi-hoan-hao-421-191303.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia: Les Bleus l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u1edd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191302.html\">Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i WC 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191301.html\">Pogba: \u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191296.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-42-croatia-421-191294.html\">HLV Croatia: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i hay ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thua Ph\u00e1p\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1291","checkdouble":"191305"},{"date":"06:19 16/07","title":"Xem l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p 4-2 Croatia qua \u1ea3nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/xem-lai-tran-chung-ket-kinh-dien-phap-42-croatia-qua-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia 4-2.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup, c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p l\u1eabn Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 sau 90 ph\u00fat h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ngay nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, khi Mario Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n&hellip; v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Croatia g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic. V\u00e0 ngay cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, Ph\u00e1p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat 11m c\u1ee7a Griezmann.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong hi\u1ec7p 2, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi 2 b\u00e0n do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe, qua \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Croatia. Cho d\u00f9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, bi\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 - Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia 4-2, chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018